{"tid":1706843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人抗爭宣言","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T07:44:22.000Z","uid":79108,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9d6eb429ca45bc6695f654518425012a85fb34","tid":1706843,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），<br />\n本人會竭誠為香港未來奮鬥，支持及維護香港的民主價值，<br />\n面對惡犬絕不畏懼、退縮。<br />\n同伴落難必伸出援手，共同退敵。<br />\n不割蓆，不督灰，並將一切榮光歸香港。<br />\n<br />\n可能大家覺得呢家做呢D好ON9, 但無奈香港好多人係咁，要靠人不斷推，先會做野。<br />\n好多人， 連今日罷工都唔撚天。<br />\n希望大家可以將呢段野放係IG. 做出個勢，為下一次鋪路。<br />\n之後大家一齊抗爭。唔撚好再做港豬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文筆差， 隨便改。"},{"pid":"1f05f181e963831b1f701241f2d6c2163c91a1e7","tid":1706843,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"d6fb536e26136218d4450b4e2b8e75a5045ad462","tid":1706843,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"6cdc6f28309c47345e3ff3c0a65756ad5b81b286","tid":1706843,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"「突發」新神獸出現，神鳥鳳凰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1706526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1706526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f67b66cbd836de9f1bc327a092967947a1a1e3be","tid":1706843,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"42479380fa1f8720a69aae1569df3879dadcd710","tid":1706843,"uid":79108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"842f97cedba442dfa4012fc37ea787805b7e41c0","tid":1706843,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"知道ON9就好"},{"pid":"e83ec82952b084ef4ce2cc83c6d680de0f748683","tid":1706843,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:36:56.00